{"title":"Brompton T Line Ceratech is the brand’s lightest-ever geared bike at 7.95kg","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/brompton-t-line-ceratech","date":1743000238000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/brompton-t-line-ceratech\">Brompton T Line Ceratech is the brand’s lightest-ever geared bike at 7.95kg</a></p>\n\n<p>Brompton has launched the T Line Ceratech, with a claimed weight starting at 7.95kg, making it its lightest ever geared bike. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>While its standard <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/brompton-titanium\">titanium T Line</a> bike comes in raw titanium colour, the Ceratech frame is surface coated with Cerakote, a thin film ceramic coating available in a range of colours, so there are now black and bronze coloured Brompton T Line frame options. You can also choose the standard titanium bike with purple parts such as the folding mechanism.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure><div></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Black-1-970x647.webp\" alt=\"Brompton T Line Ceratech\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Black-1-970x646.webp 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Black-1-300x200.webp 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Black-1-768x512.webp 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Black-1-1536x1025.webp 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Black-1-2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Black-1-750x500.webp 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Black-1-1140x760.webp 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Black-1-465x310.webp 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Black-1-620x413.webp 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Black-1-350x233.webp 350w\" /><figcaption>Brompton</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Cerakote is used for cars, aeroplanes and rockets by companies including Lamborghini, Boeing and Blue Origin. It’s ceramic-based and Brompton says it’s stronger and 62% lighter than its standard paint finish.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can choose between Brompton’s four speed and <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/brompton-12-speed\">12-speed gearing</a> options and low or mid-rise handlebars for the T Line Ceratech bike.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/subscriptions?utm_source=Web&amp;utm_medium=Banner&amp;utm_campaign=Banner+7\"><img width=\"970\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Subs-flash-162-for-web-7-970x300.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Subs-flash-162-for-web-7-970x300.webp 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Subs-flash-162-for-web-7-300x93.webp 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Subs-flash-162-for-web-7-768x238.webp 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Subs-flash-162-for-web-7-1536x476.webp 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Subs-flash-162-for-web-7-2048x634.webp 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Subs-flash-162-for-web-7-750x232.webp 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Subs-flash-162-for-web-7-1140x353.webp 1140w\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><div></div><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Bronze-4-970x647.webp\" alt=\"Brompton T Line Ceratech\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Bronze-4-970x646.webp 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Bronze-4-300x200.webp 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Bronze-4-768x512.webp 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Bronze-4-1536x1025.webp 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Bronze-4-2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Bronze-4-750x500.webp 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Bronze-4-1140x760.webp 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Bronze-4-465x310.webp 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Bronze-4-620x413.webp 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/T-Line-Ceratech-Bronze-4-350x233.webp 350w\" /><figcaption>Brompton</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The T Line comes with a carbon fork, carbon handlebars, a carbon crankset, a carbon seat post sheathed in steel and a carbon-railed saddle. Even the pedals are 15% lighter than Brompton’s standard pedals fitted to its other bikes, helping to achieve a weight figure that wouldn’t look out of place for a performance <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-road-bike\">road bike</a>.</p>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n    